.sp
You can enable this feature interactively with the
\fBtee\fR
command\&. Without a parameter, the previous file is used\&. The
\fBtee\fR
file can be disabled with the
\fBnotee\fR
command\&. Executing
\fBtee\fR
again re\-enables logging\&.
